<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verification Error</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f8fc; /* Light blue background */
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        color: #ff5733; /* Red for error */
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: #ffeb3b; /* Yellow */
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 30px;
        background-color: #ffeb3b; /* Yellow */
        color: #007bff; /* Light blue text */
        font-size: 16px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #ff9800; /* Darker yellow on hover */
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: left;
        margin-top: 40px;
        color: #888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Email Verification Failed</h1>
    <p><%= errorMessage %></p>
    <p>
      There was an issue with your email verification. Please make sure the link
      is correct or try again later.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you're still facing issues or followed the correct procedure, please
      <strong>contact us</strong> for further assistance.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you'd like to try again, you can request a new verification email
      below.
    </p>
    <a href="https://assocom.onrender.com/home" class="button"
      >Go to Home Page</a
    >

    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 AssoCom. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
